node.text: I can’t thank my fans enough for the support y’all have been giving me over the years. This win was for you. Atlanta really showed me a lot of love and I appreciate every one of you and also the people that purchased my PPV and bought tickets. Baltimore we showed out once again..I couldn’t did this without y’all.. AL HAYMON, FLOYD @floydmayweather, SHOWTIME, LIL BABY @lilbaby, my team, My family..THANK YOU!! Love 4L! 25 - 0 24 KNOCK OUTS! #TheOne #LLBB #FreeCas2x
